{"tid":158392,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"躲避盤熱爆校園 新穎又易玩","createTime":"2017-03-16T08:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T08:37:40.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"53ae3a54bad2a1c28c962a88441ab2c5bcffdc77","tid":158392,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:39:52.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>躲避盤熱爆校園 新穎又易玩<br />\n<a href=\"https://videoad.nextdigital.com.hk/apple/d_promise/13Mar2017/ver5/video.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideoad.nextdigital.com.hk%2Fapple%2Fd_promise%2F13Mar2017%2Fver5%2Fvideo.html&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG19r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=4d0db919\" target=\"_blank\">https://videoad.nextdigital.com.hk/apple/d_promise/13Mar2017/ver5/video.html</a></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n香港學生普遍都有「幾技傍身」，除了學業也經常參與各種課外活動。最近各大校園便興起一個新潮的「躲避盤」運動，簡單易學又可以減壓，讓同學既可強身健體，又能培養隊員之間合作精神及策略運用，真正有益身心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://videoad.nextdigital.com.hk/apple/d_promise/13Mar2017/ver5/images/0000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideoad.nextdigital.com.hk%2Fapple%2Fd_promise%2F13Mar2017%2Fver5%2Fimages%2F0000.jpg&h=439f5ca3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n躲避盤比賽場面<br />\n<br />\n躲避盤最先在日本興起，再經台灣傳入香港，引入香港短短兩年，已經有多間學校參與。基督教香港信義會北區青少年綜合服務中心更大力推廣躲避盤，中心主任馮佩認為此運動限制少優點多：「躲避盤好玩之處是節奏明快兼且要動腦筋，容易學又安全，加上可以訓練團隊精神及對場地要求不高，所以吸引到越來越多學校參與，不少家長也齊齊參與，絕對稱得上『老少咸宜』！」"},{"pid":"3baa425de0fe4f478a48681901a6f34dbf83a802","tid":158392,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:41:58.000Z","msg":"腳呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9df80a2a012201545521262c1673e22c4c30360","tid":158392,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:17:22.000Z","msg":"同躲避球有乜分別?"},{"pid":"bd4f3d229b93c68eb1903b85e62c26cec24d5250","tid":158392,"uid":152205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9df80a2a012201545521262c1673e22c4c30360","tid":158392,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:17:22.000Z","msg":"同躲避球有乜分別?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T08:37:40.000Z","msg":"躲避盤用一隻270mm嘅軟式飛盤（材料：尼龍、泡綿）優點：安全、刺激、講求技術，不太容易有力量差距<br />\n<br />\n適合：男女老幼<br />\n躲避球是用軟排球優點：刺激、講求力量<br />\n<br />\n適合：青少年"}]}